milestones.description: Warnapura has become the top scorer for SL in ODIs with 170 runs, going past Tennekoon's 137
Warnapura has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (40) in an innings in ODIs for SL, going past Wettimuny's 32
This is the lowest match aggregate (345) involving teams Pakistan & Sri Lanka in ODIs
Roy Dias and Warnapura's 139-run partnership is SL's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 96 between Wettimuny and Roy Dias
Javed Miandad has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (30) for PAK, going past Wasim Raja
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for SL, going past Warnapura
Roy Dias and Warnapura's 139-run partnership is SL's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 96 between Roy Dias and Wettimuny
